  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Save Your Kingdom. Survive the Chaos.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face thousands of monsters in a fast-paced pixel art action roguelite. Can you endure the unforgiving landscapes and the deadly creatures that roam them Find out in this intense and endlessly replayable adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990580/extras/1fc778f0bebbab5f515a35de4f8dad2d.poster.avif?t=1764762930\" width=800 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990580/extras/1fc778f0bebbab5f515a35de4f8dad2d.webm?t=1764762930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990580/extras/1fc778f0bebbab5f515a35de4f8dad2d.mp4?t=1764762930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn experience quickly as you battle through endless waves of enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new and powerful skills as your character levels up</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990580/extras/05b198a44cc0f104f3a1d72a0db99724.poster.avif?t=1764762930\" width=800 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990580/extras/05b198a44cc0f104f3a1d72a0db99724.webm?t=1764762930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990580/extras/05b198a44cc0f104f3a1d72a0db99724.mp4?t=1764762930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full controller support for a seamless experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine weapons and shields to create unique combat builds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a diverse cast of characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as more than 10 unlockable heroes</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990580/extras/253eaf121f5e2f7798ffac1cc1021f06.poster.avif?t=1764762930\" width=800 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990580/extras/253eaf121f5e2f7798ffac1cc1021f06.webm?t=1764762930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990580/extras/253eaf121f5e2f7798ffac1cc1021f06.mp4?t=1764762930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 100 hours of replayability through progression and randomness</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore more than 30 distinct and challenging maps</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Merge. Slay. Repeat.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Medieval Chaos is a pixel art roguelike focused on high action, unpredictable loadouts and fast build crafting. Fight swarms of enemies, unlock upgrades, and forge powerful combinations as you push through increasingly intense battles.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Weapon Merge System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine swords, spells, bows and unconventional weapons to create stronger hybrid tools mid run. Each merge opens new strategies and explosive results.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Endless Enemy Waves</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive relentless hordes in constantly shifting arenas. Dodge, strike and grow stronger as the pressure increases.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Chaos Every Time You Play</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedural maps, randomized upgrades and dynamic encounters ensure that each run feels fresh and entirely different.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>For Fans Of</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vampire Survivors, Brotato, Soulstone Survivors, 20 Minutes Till Dawn</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Save Your Kingdom. Survive the Chaos.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face thousands of monsters in a fast-paced pixel art action roguelite. Can you endure the unforgiving landscapes and the deadly creatures that roam them Find out in this intense and endlessly replayable adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990580/extras/1fc778f0bebbab5f515a35de4f8dad2d.poster.avif?t=1764762930\" width=800 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990580/extras/1fc778f0bebbab5f515a35de4f8dad2d.webm?t=1764762930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990580/extras/1fc778f0bebbab5f515a35de4f8dad2d.mp4?t=1764762930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn experience quickly as you battle through endless waves of enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new and powerful skills as your character levels up</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990580/extras/05b198a44cc0f104f3a1d72a0db99724.poster.avif?t=1764762930\" width=800 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990580/extras/05b198a44cc0f104f3a1d72a0db99724.webm?t=1764762930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990580/extras/05b198a44cc0f104f3a1d72a0db99724.mp4?t=1764762930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full controller support for a seamless experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine weapons and shields to create unique combat builds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a diverse cast of characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as more than 10 unlockable heroes</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990580/extras/253eaf121f5e2f7798ffac1cc1021f06.poster.avif?t=1764762930\" width=800 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990580/extras/253eaf121f5e2f7798ffac1cc1021f06.webm?t=1764762930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990580/extras/253eaf121f5e2f7798ffac1cc1021f06.mp4?t=1764762930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 100 hours of replayability through progression and randomness</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore more than 30 distinct and challenging maps</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Merge. Slay. Repeat.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Medieval Chaos is a pixel art roguelike focused on high action, unpredictable loadouts and fast build crafting. Fight swarms of enemies, unlock upgrades, and forge powerful combinations as you push through increasingly intense battles.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Weapon Merge System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine swords, spells, bows and unconventional weapons to create stronger hybrid tools mid run. Each merge opens new strategies and explosive results.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Endless Enemy Waves</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive relentless hordes in constantly shifting arenas. Dodge, strike and grow stronger as the pressure increases.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Chaos Every Time You Play</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedural maps, randomized upgrades and dynamic encounters ensure that each run feels fresh and entirely different.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>For Fans Of</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vampire Survivors, Brotato, Soulstone Survivors, 20 Minutes Till Dawn</p>",
